items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/The Expanse/S04/The EXPANSE - S04 E06 - Displacement (720p - AMZN Web-DL).mp4
items.summary: The Roci crew prepares for an incoming disaster on Ilus. Ashford and Drummer close in on an enemy within the Belt. Bobbie takes on a dangerous job.
items.title: Displacement

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/The Expanse/S04/The EXPANSE - S04 E07 - A Shot in The Dark (720p - AMZN Web-DL).mp4
items.summary: Naomi and Alex work to keep the Barbapiccola in orbit amidst a power outage. Avasarala faces a tough decision. Holden and Elvi race to find a cure for a disease spreading on Ilus.
items.title: A Shot in the Dark

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/The Expanse/S04/The EXPANSE - S04 E08 - The One-Eyed Man (720p - AMZN Web-DL).mp4
items.summary: Avasarala faces fallout for the UN's military mission. Ashford and Drummer makes big decisions about their future within the OPA. A spreading illness on Ilus takes a toll on Amos. Alex and Naomi's attempt to rescue the Barb turns desperate.
items.title: The One-Eyed Man

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/The Expanse/S04/The EXPANSE - S04 E09 - Saeculum (720p - AMZN Web-DL).mp4
items.summary: Holden and Miller race to save Ilus. Murtry puts his endgame into motion, putting the Roci crew's lives at risk.
items.title: Saeculum

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/The Expanse/S04/The EXPANSE - S04 E10 - Cibola Burn (720p - AMZN Web-DL).mp4
items.summary: Ashford closes in on an enemy while uncovering a dangerous plot. Avasarala faces a crossroads in her personal and political life. The Roci crew works to reestablish life on Ilus in the wake of a deadly catastrophe.
items.title: Cibola Burn

items.summary: Holden tries to convince Fred Johnson to destroy the last sample of protomolecule. Naomi gets an important lead to her son. On Luna, Avasarala begins to hunt for Marco Inaros.
items.title: Exodus

items.summary: Holden and Fred deal with infiltrators on Tycho. Drummer's past comes back to haunt her. Amos returns to Baltimore. Alex and Bobbie's investigation on Mars leads to rogue soldiers.
items.title: Churn

items.summary: Naomi comes face to face with Filip. Holden and Fred turn the tables. Avasarala closes in on Marco's plot.
items.title: Mother

items.summary: Marco's grand plan shocks Earth, Mars and the Belt.
items.title: Gaugamela

items.summary: Amos and Clarissa are trapped in a collapsed building. Naomi contends with her old family. Holden assembles a new crew on the Roci. Alex and Bobbie make a dangerous discovery in the Belt.
items.title: Down and Out

items.summary: Holden and the Roci go on the hunt. Amos and Clarissa seek shelter on a devastated Earth. Bobbie and Alex fight a desperate battle. Marco makes Drummer an offer she can't refuse. Avasarala returns to a position of power.
items.title: Tribes

items.summary: Naomi makes a desperate attempt to save her son from Marco. On the Roci, Holden battles for the last sample of protomolecule.
items.title: Oyedeng

items.summary: Amos returns to Baltimore with Clarissa. On Luna, Avasarala's alliances begin to shift. Alone and adrift, Naomi becomes a deadly lure.
items.title: Hard Vacuum

items.summary: Amos, Clarissa, and a gang of thieves work together to leave Earth. Avasarala tries to head off a brutal military strike. Drummer's new family bonds are tested as Naomi's life hangs in the balance.
items.title: Winnipesaukee

items.summary: Holden and the Roci face off against Marco's forces and Drummer, while Alex and Bobbie attempt a dangerous rescue of Naomi, and the balance of power in the Solar System shifts.
items.title: Nemesis Games

items.summary: The crew of Serenity take on a train heist commissioned by a crime lord. They steal the goods, only to find it is medicine that's desperately needed by the town.
items.title: The Train Job

items.summary: Serenity is pulled in by a Tohoku-class cruiser while investigating a spaceship that was attacked by Reavers. Simon and River must hide to prevent capture, while something is wrong with the lone survivor of the attacked spaceship.
items.title: Bushwhacked

items.summary: As an unexpected reward for an unpaid job, Mal finds himself married to a naïve, subservient young woman named Saffron. The crew are amused at his discomfort and Book lectures him on propriety, but things aren't as smoothly straightforward as they thought them to be.
items.title: Our Mrs. Reynolds

items.summary: Returning to a planet where he ran into some serious trouble years ago, Jayne discovers that he's become a local folk legend. Mal decides to use this entertaining distraction to complete a job, but some unfinished business may derail his plans.
items.title: Jaynestown

items.summary: After Serenity suffers a catastrophe that leaves her crew with only hours of oxygen, flashbacks show how Mal and Zoë acquired Serenity and assembled their motley band.
items.title: Out of Gas

items.summary: Inara attends a formal society dance, only to find Malcolm there as well, attempting to set up a smuggling job. Mal comes to blows with Inara's conceited date and finds himself facing a duel with a renowned swordsman, and only one night to learn how to fence.
items.title: Shindig

items.summary: Mal must choose which crew members to save when one is gravely wounded and two others are kidnapped. Simon finds an uneasy haven in a remote village, but River's uncanny perceptions jeopardize the Tams' temporary safety.
items.title: Safe

items.summary: Hard up for cash, Serenity takes on a job from Simon: help him get a thorough diagnostic of River in return for the opportunity to loot the vast medical stores of an Alliance hospital on central world Ariel. But River's pursuers are hot on their trail, and they receive some unexpected inside help.
items.title: Ariel

items.summary: Angered at Zoë's unshakable war connection to Mal, Wash demands a shot at a field assignment. Unfortunately, crime lord Niska chooses this moment to exact a brutal vengeance for Mal's failure to complete an earlier job.
items.title: War Stories

items.summary: Serenity encounters a ruthlessly professional bounty hunter, Jubal Early, who will stop at nothing to retrieve River. But River, feeling unwelcome on the ship, takes a novel approach to escaping from the long arm of the Alliance.
items.title: Objects in Space

items.summary: Malcolm Reynolds is a veteran and the captain of Serenity. He and his crew are smuggling goods, but they need to pick up some passengers for extra money. However, not all the passengers are what they seem.
items.title: Serenity

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 01 - Through the Eye of the Needle TSV.mkv
items.summary: Astronaut John Crichton attempts to use the Earth's atmosphere to propel his module at high speeds. He is hit by a radiation wave and is sucked through a wormhole into a distant part of the universe--straight into the middle of a space battle.
items.title: Premiere

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 02 - I, E.T. TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya gets infested with bugs who have come on board to breed. They turn up the temperature to speed up the process but this causes Aeryn to get heat delirium as she is cold blooded. The bugs seem to be able to replicate members of the crew. And as if that isn't enough, a peacekeeper ship shows up.
items.title: Exodus from Genesis

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 03 - Exodus from Genesis TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew come across a ship that is molecularly de-stabilizing. D'Argo makes everyone bring it aboard when he discovers that there are Ilanics on board. Crichton goes on to the escape pod he gets a shock and starts experiencing strange visions of the future, firstly of himself and Matala, then of Moya's destruction.
items.title: Back and Back and Back to the Future
items.titleSort: Back and Back and Back to the Future

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 04 - Throne for a Loss TSV.mkv
items.summary: A group of Tavleks come aboard for trade negotiations. Rygel takes a vitally important crystal from Moya to make himself seem wealthy. The Tavleks kidnap Rygel and take him down to the planet, leaving one of their wounded on board. Everyone goes to the surface to get him except Zhaan who stays on board to keep an eye on the Tavlek left behind.
items.title: Throne for a Loss

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 05 - Back and Back and Back to the Future TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew find an old abandoned peacekeeper ship adrift in space, on board they discover that Crais was there recently where he deposited a unit of techs to make repairs. Meanwhile Rygel learns that this was the ship where he was first held captive and starts getting paranoid. Things get even worse though when a group of fire breathing aliens show up.
items.title: PK Tech Girl

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 06 - Thank God It's Friday, Again TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew visits a planet full of happy workers. Soon D'Argo and Zhaan start working and refuse to return to the ship. Meanwhile Rygel's body fluids become explosive and Aeryn and Pilot must learn why before Rygel dies.
items.title: Thank God It's Friday, Again

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 07 - PK Tech Girl TSV.mkv
items.summary: A peacekeeper beacon goes off and Moya has to land on an alien planet to prevent it's signal being intercepted and Moya being discovered. Crichton, D'Argo and Aeryn leave Moya and explore the planet in search of a substance that can be used to numb Moya's senses so the beacon can be removed. Crichton gets separated from the group and meets up with some inhabitants of the planet who hide him from the authorities.
items.title: I, E.T.

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 08 - That Old Black Magic TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton is put into a head-to-head battle with Crais by a magical being named Maldis who feeds off the emotions of others and makes himself stronger by absorbing all of the negative energy and anger from Crichton and Crais.
items.title: That Old Black Magic

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 09 - DNA Mad Scientist TSV.mkv
items.summary: A scientist extracts DNA from several of Moya's crew, promising them that with it he would be able to use it to find the location of their home planets. Things get more interesting however when he asks for some of pilot.
items.title: DNA Mad Scientist

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 10 - They Have Got A Secret TSV.mkv
items.summary: During routine searches for Peacekeeper beacons, D'Argo falls down a chute, destroys a Peacekeeper shield and gets ejected into open space. After being rescued D'Argo starts to think that everyone on Moya are members of his family. Moya, meanwhile, starts to alter the environmental conditions inside the ship so that it is hardly habitable for the crew. .
items.title: They've Got a Secret

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 11 - Til The Blood Runs Clear TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton comes across the same conditions that initially created a wormhole. He leaves Moya in his module with Aeryn where he attempts to create a wormhole and return home. Although a wormhole forms it is unstable and the module gets damaged and he is forced to make an emergency landing on the planet to make repairs. On the planet he and Aeryn encounter a holographic message sent by Crais, offering rewards for: D'Argo, Zhaan and Rygel.
items.title: Till the Blood Runs Clear

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 12 - Rhapsody In Blue TSV.mkv
items.summary: While on a transport pod piloting lesson with Aeryn, Crichton gets caught in an energy field which is invisible to their sensors. Back on Moya, a strange guest docks and comes aboard to warn the crew about The Flax, an invisible energy net created to catch ships.
items.title: The Flax

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 13 - The Flax TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya responds to a distress call from another pregnant Leviathan. On arrival at a planet they are contacted by a Delvian who informs them that the distress call was a deception. It was her way a getting Moya to come to them. The Delvians have a hidden agenda though. They want to forcefully take Zhaan's knowledge and learn how she overcame her insanity.
items.title: Rhapsody in Blue

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 14 - Jeremiah Crichton TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton leaves Moya in his module for a drive. Moya starbursts leaving Crichton marooned and alone in space. He finds a planet and makes it his home where he lives for several months until the others find him. He is unwilling to accept however, that Moya didn't starburst intentionally.
items.title: Jeremiah Crichton

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 15 - Durka Returns TSV.mkv
items.summary: When a Starburst goes badly wrong, Moya collides with a Nebari ship. On board is Durka, Rygel's former torturer, who has been mind cleansed and now serves the Nebari. Chiana, an attractive young rebel faces the same fate. Rygel takes it upon himself to take revenge on Durka and ends up undoing the cleansing and restoring him to his former, tyrannic incarnation.
items.title: Durka Returns

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 16 - A Human Reaction TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton is sucked down a wormhole and crash lands on a beach...on Earth, Australia. Although the home he has returned to isn't as real as it seems. Everything gets worse when the rest of Moya's crew shows up and are experimented on...killing Rygel.
items.title: A Human Reaction

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 17 - Through The Looking Glass TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya tries to starburst to prove to the crew that she still can. It goes slightly wrong though and she gets stuck in starburst and split into several different dimensions.
items.title: Through the Looking Glass

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 18 - A Bug's Life TSV.mkv
items.summary: A peacekeeper ship is approaching Moya, so Crichton and Aeryn pose as peacekeeper officers on a secret mission while everyone else gets locked into cells to make the deception seem realistic. The peacekeepers that come aboard have some secret cargo. But when their secret cargo escapes, no one on board is safe.
items.title: A Bug's Life

items.summary: Crichton and Chiana try to infiltrate a peacekeeper base to get some vital medicine for Aeryn. Crichton gets caught by Scorpius and imprisoned. He is tortured using a device called the 'Aurora Chair' which is able to look inside his mind and where Scorpius learns that Crichton has the secret to creating wormholes.
items.title: Nerve

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 20 - The Hidden Memory TSV.mkv
items.summary: Scorpius attempts to extract the wormhole technology from Crichton's mind, while Aeryn mounts a rescue operation. Crais finds himself at Scorpius' mercy, and Moya gives birth.
items.title: The Hidden Memory

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 21 - Bone to be Wild TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya is hiding from a peacekeeper command carrier in an asteroid field. The crew receive a distress call and Crichton, Zhaan and D'Argo go down to one of the asteroids to rescue a women who has an unusual appetite.
items.title: Bone to Be Wild

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 01/Farscape Season 01 Episode 22 - Family Ties TSV.mkv
items.summary: Rygel steals a transport pod and goes to the peacekeeper command carrier to betray the others. However he ends up returning to Moya with Crais who wants asylum. Crichton decides to destroy Scorpius' Gamac Base to give Moya time to escape.
items.title: Family Ties

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 01 - Mind The Baby TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton, Aeryn and D'argo are stranded in an asteroid field while Scorpius searches for them. Their safety depends on Crais, who is nearby in Talyn. Aeryn teaches Crais how to control the young Leviathan - the only thing she can offer in return for the lives of her friends. When Moya returns to the asteroid field to look for her offspring, Crichton decides to remove Crais from control of Talyn. Scorpius finally sees his chance to strike.
items.title: Mind the Baby

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 02 - Vitas Mortis TSV.mkv
items.summary: D'Argo takes part in a sacred ritual that helps an old Luxan, an Orican, to survive. During the ritual the Orican draws energy from who she thinks is D'Argo but is actually Moya. Consequently Moya starts to age rapidly.
items.title: Vitas Mortis

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 03 - Taking the Stone TSV.mkv
items.summary: Chiana leaves Moya and goes to 'grave planet' populated by reckless thrill seekers who play dangerous and life threatening games.
items.title: Taking the Stone

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 04 - Crackers Don't Matter TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew returns from a Commerce Planet with a load of Crackers and a meek alien called Traltixx, who promises he can alter Moya's electromagnetics to make her untraceable. Crichton is skeptical; it seems too good to be true. As they pass through a constellation of pulsars, an intense paranoia affects the crew, turning them violently again each other. Crichton must fight against his own paranoid delusions to work out what Traltixx is actually doing and how to stop him.
items.title: Crackers Don't Matter

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 05 - Picture If You Will TSV.mkv
items.summary: A datacam tape is uncovered showing Aeryn as part of a Peacekeeper firing squad that executed a previous Pilot aboard Moya. The rest of the crew wants answers but Aeryn is recalcitrant about revisiting her past - especially her relationship with Velorek, the man charged with forcibly bonding a new Pilot to Moya. Pilot two refuses to communicate with the crew, not wanting to reveal his own complicity in the murky circumstances surrounding his installment as Moya's guide.
items.title: The Way We Weren't

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 06 - The Way We Weren't TSV.mkv
items.summary: Maldus returns to torment the crew, convincing them that their friends have perished. One by one, the evil sorcerer drags them into his realm.
items.title: Picture if You Will

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 07 - Home On The Remains TSV.mkv
items.summary: With Moya out of food, Chiana leads everyone to a dead boudong where she once worked.
items.title: Home on the Remains

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 08 - Dream a Little Dream TSV.mkv
items.summary: While waiting inside a transport pod to be picked up by Moya, Zhaan tells Crichton about being accused and tried for murder during his absence.
items.title: Dream a Little Dream

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 09 - Out Of Their Minds TSV.mkv
items.summary: An alien ship fires a weapon at Moya. Although the energy shield is active, some of the blast makes it through and causes everyone's consciousness to jump into another body.
items.title: Out of Their Minds

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 10 - My Three Crichtons TSV.mkv
items.summary: A strange globe appears on Moya, sucking in Crichton and duplicating him creating two additional people. One who is a de-evolved 'cave man' and another who has increased mental ability.
items.title: My Three Crichtons

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 11 - Look at the Princess (Part 1) A Kiss is But a Kiss TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya arrives at a planet where the population test their genetic compatibility by kissing. Crichton kisses a princess, who is next in line for the throne, and discovers that his DNA is a perfect match for her. He must now marry her and they will rule together.
items.title: Look at the Princess - A Kiss is But a Kiss (1)
items.titleSort: Look at the Princess - A Kiss is But a Kiss (1)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 12 - Look at the Princess (Part 2) I Do, I Think TSV.mkv
items.summary: Princess Katralla's mother brings in Scorpius promising Crichton that if he doesn't marry her daughter, she will hand him over. Meanwhile, Prince Clavor starts a plot to assassinate Crichton so that he may ascend to the throne instead of his sister.
items.title: Look at the Princess - I Do, I Think (2)
items.titleSort: Look at the Princess - I Do, I Think (2)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 13 - Look at the Princess (Part 3) The Maltese Crichton TSV.mkv
items.summary: Now married, Crichton and Katalla are frozen into living statues so that they may watch over the presiding governments of the next eighty cycles. Immediately, Clavor and the Scarran emissary attempt another assassination and succeed in removing Crichton's head. The crew must save John and Chiana while escaping Scorpius.
items.title: Look at the Princess - The Maltese Crichton (3)
items.titleSort: Look at the Princess - The Maltese Crichton (3)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 14 - Beware Of Dog TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew bring aboard an alien tracker to remove some creatures that came aboard hidden in some cargo.
items.title: Beware of Dog

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 15 - Won't Get Fooled Again TSV.mkv
items.summary: The Scorpius clone puts John into a dream world to prevent the Scarrans from getting any wormhole knowledge.
items.title: Won't Get Fooled Again

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 16 - The Locket TSV.mkv
items.summary: A temporal distortion traps Aeryn and John on a planet's surface, where they live out the rest of their lives -- while Moya remains trapped in orbit, experiencing only hours. Stark returns to the ship with news of D'Argo's son.
items.title: The Locket

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 17 - The Ugly Truth TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crais and Talyn return. The crew are put on trial for an attack that Talyn made on an alien ship.
items.title: The Ugly Truth

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 18 - A Clockwork Nebari TSV.mkv
items.summary: A Nebari group come aboard Moya and attempt to mind cleanse everyone using a drug. Pilot and Rygel are the only two who can resist the effects. Crichton also remains unaffected due to Scorpius' neural clone.
items.title: A Clockwork Nebari

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 19 - Liars, Guns and Money (Part 1) A Not So Simple Plan TSV.mkv
items.summary: Stark returns to Moya with a plan to rob a shadow depository and buy a contingent of slaves, one of which is D'Argo's son Jothee. D'Argo attempts the robbery on his own however and now the crew must recover him as well as the money they require.
items.title: Liars, Guns and Money - A Not So Simple Plan (1)
items.titleSort: Liars, Guns and Money - A Not So Simple Plan (1)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 20 - Liars, Guns and Money (Part 2) With Friends Like These TSV.mkv
items.summary: Scorpius buys the slaves containing D'Argo's son before D'Argo can. Some of the crew leave Moya in search of mercenaries to rescue Jothee. Meanwhile back on Moya, the stolen money has turned into metal eating spiders that begin to consume Moya.
items.title: Liars, Guns and Money - With Friends Like These... (2)
items.titleSort: Liars, Guns and Money - With Friends Like These... (2)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 21 - Liars, Guns and Money (Part 3) Plan B TSV.mkv
items.summary: Crichton turns himself over to Scorpius in order to free Jothee. With all the mercenaries now aboard Moya, the crew form a plan to rescue Crichton and destroy the depository.
items.title: Liars, Guns and Money - Plan B (3)
items.titleSort: Liars, Guns and Money - Plan B (3)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 02/Farscape Season 02 Episode 22 - Die Me Dichotomy TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew find a doctor that can heal Moya's burns and remove Crichton's neural chip. Things are complicated however when Crichton is informed he needs additional brain tissue from a donor in stasis who will die when the tissue is removed. Also Scorpius is beginning to take over Crichton's brain.
items.title: Die Me, Dichotomy

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 01 - Season of Death TSV.mkv
items.summary: D'Argo and Stark try to heal John, left with his head open on an operating table, while Scorpius attempts to avoid discovery. Zhaan makes a great personal sacrifice, while Jothee and Chiana commit an indiscretion.
items.title: Season of Death

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 02 - Suns and Lovers TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya docks at a commerce station so the crew can spend some of the money they acquired from the depository. Disaster strikes however when the station is hit by a storm.
items.title: Suns and Lovers

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 03 - Self-Inflicted Wounds (Part 1) - Coulda, Woulda, Shoulda TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya approaches a wormhole, gets pulled in and fused to another ship.
items.title: Self-Inflicted Wounds - Could'a, Would'a, Should'a (1)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 04 - Self-Inflicted Wounds (Part 2) - Wait for the Wheel TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew work out a way of getting free from the other ship and out of the wormhole. Things become more complicated when their new 'friends' begin to sabotage Moya and Crichton picks up a transmission from Earth.
items.title: Self-Inflicted Wounds - Wait for the Wheel (2)
items.titleSort: Self-Inflicted Wounds - Wait for the Wheel (2)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 05 - Different Destinations TSV.mkv
items.summary: Stark accidentally sends himself, Crichton, Aeryn and Jool back in time where they alter the time line and are forced to interfere further to restore it.
items.title: ...Different Destinations

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 06 - Eat Me TSV.mkv
items.summary: In need of supplies, Crichton lands his transport pod on a dying leviathan which is full of hungry cannibals and a scientist who has the ability to create clones.
items.title: Eat Me

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 07 - Thanks  For Sharing TSV.mkv
items.summary: Moya rendezvous with Talyn who is seriously damaged. They hide in the atmosphere of a planet to prevent the Peacekeepers from finding them. D'Argo and Rygel go down to the planet to find some Clorium, a drug that will help Talyn recover.
items.title: Thanks for Sharing

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 08 - Green Eyed Monster TSV.mkv
items.summary: Talyn is swallowed by a boodong, leaving Stark and Rygel stranded in a transport pod.
items.title: Green Eyed Monster

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 09 - Losing Time TSV.mkv
items.summary: The crew of Moya start blacking out and missing portions of time. Pilot becomes inhabited by another entity who needs to 'taste' each crew member to determine if they too are being inhabited.
items.title: Losing Time

items.summary: Talyn lands on a planet covered mostly with vegetation that will help him to heal. Crichton, Aeryn and Crais leave the ship in search of Xhalax.
items.title: Relativity

items.summary: Scorpius puts the neural chip into his own brain in an attempt to retrieve vital wormhole equations from Crichton.
items.title: Incubator

items.summary: Talyn gets the urge to fly into a sun. While in its vicinity Stark is contacted by an alien women who is being held against her will.
items.title: Meltdown

items.summary: Crichton, D'Argo, Jool and Chiana are forced to take a holiday by Pilot as he is fed up with their constant bickering.
items.title: Scratch 'n Sniff

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 14 - Infinite Possibilities (Part 1) - Daedalus Demands TSV.mkv

items.title: Infinite Possibilities - Daedalus Demands (1)

items.summary: Jack (The Ancient) unlocks the wormhole knowledge in Crichton's mind so together they can build a device to destroy the Scarran dreadnought.
items.title: Infinite Possibilities - Icarus Abides (2)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 16 - Revenging Angel TSV.mkv
items.summary: There is an accident while D'Argo is demonstrating what his ship can do. He blames Crichton and knocks him out. In his unconscious state Crichton has some animated dreams.
items.title: Revenging Angel

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 17 - The Choice TSV.mkv
items.summary: Aeryn goes to a planet in search of someone who can contact her father.
items.title: The Choice

items.summary: A group of escaped prisoners come aboard Moya followed shortly by Aeryn, Stark, Crais and Rygel who have finally returned from Talyn.
items.title: Fractures

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 19 - I Yensch, You Yensch TSV.mkv
items.summary: D'Argo and Rygel meet Braca and Scorpius in a cafe to conduct negotiations when it is unexpectedly attacked.
items.title: I-Yensch, You-Yensch

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 20 - Into the Lion's Den (Part 1) - Lambs To The Slaughter TSV.mkv

items.title: Into the Lion's Den - Lambs to the Slaughter (1)
items.titleSort: Into the Lion's Den - Lambs to the Slaughter (1)

items.locations: /volume1/PLEX_MEDIA/TV Shows/Farscape/Season 03/Farscape Season 03 Episode 21 - Into the Lion's Den (Part 2) - Wolf In Sheep's Clothing TSV.mkv
